Package: pyxkeyboard
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3-pyqt6, python3-xlib, x11-xkb-utils, python3-gi, gir1.2-atspi-2.0
Description: On-screen virtual keyboard with layout switching
 A simple, customizable on-screen virtual keyboard for Linux (X11/Xorg).
 Features include:
  * Typing via XTEST simulation.
  * System keyboard layout switching (via setxkbmap).
  * Visual feedback for the current layout (EN/AR).
  * Modifier key support (Shift, Ctrl, Alt, Caps Lock).
  * Resizable.
  * Easy Movable.
  * System tray integration.
  * Customizable appearance (font, opacity, colors).
  * Optional auto-show when focusing text fields (via AT-SPI).
